    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note>Il <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arechi II</persName> offre
                            al monastero di S. Sofia di <placeName
                                key="#Uncertain_tradition #Cities #Fiscal_property #Nuns/sanctimoniales"
                                ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> (prosegue l'elenco iniziato
                            con il doc. 3535):</note></ab>
                    <ab>(…) [19] Seu et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >substantia</rs>
                        <name ref="Aliperga">Aliperge</name>
                        <rs key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales">ancelle Dei</rs> que derelicto religionis
                        habitu <name ref="Taurus">Tauro</name> filius <name ref="Ramfus"
                            >Ramfoni</name> inlicito se tradedit matrimonio, unde secundum edicti
                        tenore omnis eius <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >substantia</rs> ad nostra est devoluta potestate, nostra vero potestas
                        omnia eius nominate Aliperge substantię in integrum cum ipsa Aliperga
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                            key="#Property_of_criminals/political_traitors #Monasteries">Sancte
                            Sophie <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs></orgName> tradedimus
                        possidendum. (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p><emph>Editions</emph>: IS1 VIII, col. 575D-576A; IS2 VIII, col. 29A-B; IS2 X-2,
