                    [19], pp. 304-305 (source of the text reproduced here). <emph>Document
                        summaries</emph>: Di Meo 1795-1819, III, p. 95; RIM, 426 (v. 367).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p>De Vita 1764, p. 294; Bertolini O, 1926, 72.</p>
            </div>
